item.title: `Carrion 317~~ The next generation in 317 Skilling
item.dc:creator: @mursanari mursanari
item.description:
@mursanari wrote:

Introduction;

Carrion 317, the re-birth of the delta generation.
You might be thinking “Facepalm, another badly coded delta” But its really anything but that.

Origins;

Carrion (car-re-on) means, Corrupted or rotting flesh, i thought it might be a good idea for a server name because of the song “Carrion” by “Parkway Drive” One of Australia’s most famous bands (i’m from australia btw)

Features;

Carrion boasts almost all of the 317 skills these include,
Runecrafting
Agility
Thieving
Crafting
Fletching
Mining
Smithing
Fishing
Firemaking
Woodcutting
Farming

Carrion also offers many quests for the adventurers wich are
Rune mysteries
Sheep Shearer
Desert Treasure
Vampire Slayer
Monkey Madness
Legends Quest
Knights Legend
Lunare Spirit
The wolfs cure
Rampage
Recipe for disaster
Druidic Ritual
(These quests ARENT full, they are bases of the real thing)

Carrion also offers Many minigames such as
Complete barrows with spade required
Castle wars (coming soon!)
Pest Control
Some shit Assult minigame :L

Other features;
Extremely stable
Working piety
Godswords with Stances and specs
Claws with 4 hits
Working Autocast
Most dupes fixed
Ammy teleports working

Heaps more, but thats it atm my eye is twitching and wont stop, so i’ll post pics later feel free to ask for info, i’m going to release the source to the private server community for the better of them even though all youve done is made me eat your shit. have a good day (:
